  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a equals, c plus d\"></span></span>, which of the following is equivalent to the expression <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, minus c squared, minus 2 c d, minus d squared\"></span></span>?</p>\n",
